ffer employees the opportunities they need to succeed both personally and professionally our comprehensive benefits and expansive learning and development programs together with a variety of career options make lowe’s an exceptional place to begin and grow your career  most admired company  fortune  happiest retailers to work for  go find more about looking for a company thats dedicated to its employees and their growth military are you a military veteran reservist spouse your skills and experience work here use our military skills translator to find a lowe’s opportunity that’s a perfect fit for you  the military instills leadership a strong work ethic and a passion for a job well done a testament to the “power of we” the founder of lowe’s carl buchan is a military veteran himself today lowe’s employs more than  military veterans across our organization in fields from management it and retail to customer service we continue to pursue military veterans reservists and military spouses to join our team by participating in a variety of militarysponsored programs and events across the country military friendly employer  esgr military spouse ep go find more about are you a military veteran reservist spouse diversity why we embrace diversity  inclusion lowe’s is committed to a workplace culture that leverages diverse talent to create innovative solutions   our employees thrive in an environment where everyone can reach their full potential and provide our customers with  a great shopping experience to support our commitment to maintain a diverse workforce lowe’s participates in several career conferences that engage diverse candidates such as the national black mba conference and women of color stem conference science technology engineering  mathematics check out our conference  event calendar to see if we have an upcoming event near you  champions honoree  national inclusion project go find more about why we embrace diversity  inclusion on campus still in school recently 